name: Gravitationally Drawn To This Moment In Time
description:
HEN was discontinued while I was in the process of making a new series of artwork. This sudden turbulence found it's way into a drastic shift in the final work. This piece represents a disruptive era in Hic Et Nunc, striving to show the ever shifting diversity and beauty of this DIY community.

1024 x 1024 pixels, 1 minute 13 seconds | Ryan Thompson, November 2021 | www.ryanthompson.name
